text: Colobothea osculatii is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Félix Édouard Guérin-Méneville in 1855. It is known from Ecuador and Peru.BioLib.cz - Colobothea osculatii. Retrieved 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1855
